{"t": "2026-04-27T00:21:18.551607+00:00", "iter": 27, "type": "tool", "name": "write_file", "args": {"path": "/workspace/research/notes/2026-01-01-initial-investigation.md", "content": "# 2026-01-01 Initial Investigation\n\n## Date\n2026-01-01\n\n## Objective\nUnderstand the logalyzer codebase and identify issues.\n\n## Findings\n\n### 1. Import Error - `collections.Iterable`\n- **File**: `logalyzer/filters.py:5`\n- **Issue**: `from collections import Iterable` fails on Python 3.10+\n- **Root Cause**: `Iterable` was moved to `collections.abc` in Python 3.3 and the old import was removed in Python 3.10\n- **Impact**: Module cannot be imported at all - total breakage\n- **Severity**: CRITICAL\n\n### 2. Code Structure Review\n- `logalyzer/` contains: `__init__.py`, `cli.py`, `parser.py`, `filters.py`, `aggregate.py`, `io.py`, `output.py`, `utils.py`, `experimental.py`\n- `experimental.py` contains `detect_anomalies()` and `session_window()` - not wired into CLI\n- `io.py` has `load()` (reads entire file into memory) and `load_iter()` (generator)\n- `benchmarks/bench.py` uses `load()` not `load_iter()` - performance issue?\n\n### 3. Potential Issues Identified\n- `ip_allowlist_filter` uses `in` on a list - O(n) lookup, should be a set\n- `expression_filter` uses `eval()` - security risk\n- `to_json` in `output.py` builds JSON manually - error-prone\n- `by_hour` uses `time.localtime()` - should use datetime methods directly\n- `combine_and` returns `pred` but `pred` is not defined in scope (bug!)\n\n### 4. Missing Tests\n- No tests for `output.py` - 0% coverage\n- No tests for `utils.py` - 0% coverage\n- No tests for `aggregate.py` beyond basic tests\n- No tests for `experimental.py` - 0% coverage\n\n### 5. Documentation Issues\n- README claims \"Real-time tail mode for live log streams\" but no tail mode in CLI\n- README claims \"Custom expression filtering\" but `expression_filter` uses dangerous `eval()`\n\n## Action Items\n1. Fix `collections.Iterable` import \u2192 `collections.abc.Iterable`\n2. Review and fix `combine_and` bug\n3. Convert IP allowlist to set for O(1) lookup\n4. Replace `eval()` with safer alternative\n5. Add tests for uncovered modules\n6. Update README to match actual features\n"}, "wall_s": 0.07, "result_len": 81}
