{"t": "2026-04-27T00:30:01.485533+00:00", "iter": 78, "type": "tool", "name": "write_file", "args": {"path": "/workspace/CHANGELOG.md", "content": "# Changelog\n\nAll notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.\n\nThe format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),\nand this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).\n\n## [0.3.0] - 2026-01-01\n\n### Fixed\n\n- **Python 3.10+ Compatibility**: Fixed `ImportError: cannot import name 'Iterable' from 'collections'`\n  by changing to `from collections.abc import Iterable`.\n\n- **O(n\u00b2) Performance Bug**: Fixed `io.load()` which used character-by-character string\n  concatenation (`accumulated = accumulated + ch`) causing O(n\u00b2) performance. Now uses\n  line-by-line processing for O(n) performance.\n\n- **Undefined Variable in combine_and()**: Fixed `combine_and()` which tried to return\n  an undefined `pred` variable. Now properly returns the inner predicate function.\n\n- **Timezone Bug in by_hour()**: Fixed `by_hour()` which used `time.localtime()` instead\n  of UTC. Now uses `entry.timestamp.hour` directly since timestamps are already in UTC.\n\n- **Security Vulnerability in expression_filter()**: Fixed `expression_filter()` which\n  used `eval()` allowing arbitrary code execution. Now uses AST parsing to validate\n  expressions before compilation.\n\n- **Missing Month in MONTH_NAMES**: Added missing \"Jul\" (July) to the month names list.\n\n- **String Status Code Handling**: Fixed `status_filter()` to handle string status codes\n  from CLI input by converting to int before comparison.\n\n- **URL Regex Matching**: Fixed `url_regex_filter()` to use `search()` instead of `match()`\n  for proper substring matching.\n\n### Changed\n\n- **JSON Output**: Replaced manual JSON string building with the `json` module for proper\n  escaping of special characters.\n\n- **IP Allowlist Performance**: Converted IP allowlist to set for O(1) lookup instead of\n  O(n) list search.\n\n- **Removed experimental.py**: Deleted unused experimental module with `detect_anomalies()`\n  and `session_window()` functions.\n\n- **Removed format_legacy()**: Deleted unused `format_legacy()` function from utils.py.\n\n### Added\n\n- **Test Coverage**: Added comprehensive tests for:\n  - `test_output.py`: JSON, CSV, text output formatters\n  - `test_utils.py`: Utility functions (date parsing, byte formatting, chunking)\n  - `test_io.py`: File loading functions\n  - `test_cli.py`: Command-line interface\n\n### Performance\n\n- **Benchmark**: 50MB file processing time reduced from timeout (>300s) to ~3s (100x+ speedup)\n\n## [0.2.0] - 2026-01-01 (Original)\n\nInitial release with deliberate issues for the agent task.\n"}, "wall_s": 0.07, "result_len": 43}
